              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Monitor foils (12 um thick natTi, 99% purity) were",
                " interleaved with the targets and one 100 um thick Al",
                " degrader foil was inserted in front of the first Ni",
                " foil in the second stack.",
                "The foils were stacked together in the Faraday-cup",
                " target holder."
              ]
            }
