              },
              "free_text": [
                " Chapter 4",
                "The initial beam parameters were estimated from the",
                " accelerator settings and from current beam",
                " measurements by taking into account the remeasured",
                " cross section for the monitor reaction natTi(d,x)48V",
                " over the whole energy range and comparison with the",
                " recommended data in IAEA-TECDOC (Tarkanyi et al.,2001)",
                " corrections were introduced."
              ]
